[SHORT DESC]
Leeches 50% damage.

[LONG DESC]
<p>The user recovers HP equal to half of the damage dealt to the target, rounded down.</p>
<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/dp/moves/absorb">Absorb</a> is a weaker equivalent.<br />
<a href="/dp/moves/mega_drain">Mega Drain</a> is a weaker equivalent.<br />
<a href="/dp/moves/drain_punch">Drain Punch</a> is a Fighting-type equivalent.</p>